      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:30:1",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ رَجُلٍ يَفْتَرِي كَيْفَ يَنْبَغِي لِلْإِمَامِ أَنْ يَضْرِبَهُ قَالَ جُلِدَ بَيْنَ الْجَلْدَيْنِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from Usman Bin Isa, from Sama’at Bin Mahran who said, ",
          "‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about a man who fabricated, how would it befit the Imam<sup>asws</sup> that he<sup>asws</sup> whips him?’ He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘He<sup>asws</sup> would whip him between the two whippings (between the highest and the lowest Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>))’."
        ]
      }
    }
